node1: { next: { next: {  }, value: 0 }, value: 1 }
node2: { next: { next: {  }, value: 0 }, value: 2 }
After circular assignment:
node1: { next: { next: {  }, value: 2 }, value: 1 }
node2: { next: { next: {  }, value: 1 }, value: 2 }
node1.next: { next: {  }, value: 2 }
node2.next: { next: {  }, value: 1 }
